contentrichtext.text: '''Come Back, Little Sheba''' may refer to: * [[Come Back, Little Sheba (play)|''Come Back, Little Sheba'' (play)]], a play by William Inge * [[Come Back, Little Sheba (1952 film)|''Come Back, Little Sheba'' (1952 film)]], a film based on the play, starring Burt Lancaster and Shirley Booth * [[Come Back, Little Sheba (1977 TV drama)|''Come Back, Little Sheba'' (1977 TV drama)]], an adaptation of the play, starring Laurence Olivier and Joanne Woodward * "Come Back Little Sheba", a song by Patti Smith, a B-side from the single "[[Summer Cannibals]]" {{disambig}}
